OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry, bright and very
OL,6,Fwarm day across the south of region.
OL,7,FFurther north, turning increasingly
OL,8,Fcloudy with some rain in Cumbria and
OL,9,Fperhaps parts of Lancashire. This can
OL,10,Fbe heavy at times and can move
OL,11,Fsouthwards.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain eases and becomes more
OL,14,Fconfined to hill of Cumbria. Staying
OL,15,Fcloud across the north with clearer
OL,16,Fspells in the south. A mild night to
OL,17,Fcome for most places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
