OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother dry start to the day
OL,6,Fwith bright spells in the south and
OL,7,Fmore in the way of cloud in the north.
OL,8,FTurning wetter here into the late
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,12,Fmore settled into the weekend as high
OL,13,Fpressure starts to build from the
OL,14,Fsouth. Sunny spells and feeling very
OL,15,Fwarm with temperatures well above the
OL,16,FJune average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
